{"tid":577761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同事把口極臭 點算","createTime":"2018-03-02T04:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T05:35:44.000Z","uid":115090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9805ec5ccbf7b8ebdc46ccceca93502943261045","tid":577761,"uid":115090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:41:04.000Z","msg":"有位同事個口發出惡臭<br />\n平時同佢講野已經隔開啲距離嫁啦<br />\n點知最近嚴重咗 <br />\n日日朝早開會 隔住張大枱嘅距離都聞到<br />\n仲要佢係負責hold會 有9成時間都係佢講野<br />\n係臭到我完全集中唔到精神<br />\n不自覺咁皺曬眉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果佢以為我黑佢面 唔鍾意佢<br />\n又成日走黎關心我 問我野<br />\n我已經每次佢講野嘅時間整下個鼻 撥下手咁樣<br />\n到底仲可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d76f13b7e4146e21bb58b7c9a2b9121a09bde3","tid":577761,"uid":53254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"撥手是性暗示"},{"pid":"9f04b32878aa6237811cb0c38418eab14577d130","tid":577761,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  食煙食到勁口臭"},{"pid":"b74809e22274afaa7c059eac4b97676af1115638","tid":577761,"uid":61177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"我有個同事個口又係勁撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢前排病左戴口罩<br />\n隔住個口罩都聞到陣惡臭<br />\n唔知以為佢收埋條屍係個口到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2798be10c64b2fcb8303faf9e073ae06f17c987c","tid":577761,"uid":53554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cb61d15ee349cb947d1f4eb04fefced60c02c07","tid":577761,"uid":115090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b74809e22274afaa7c059eac4b97676af1115638","tid":577761,"uid":61177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:46:56.000Z","